INSERT INTO tGastExamples VALUES ('z2DCebolla', 'cebollasample', '~#javaj#~6~6    <frames> f1,~6~6    <layout of f1>~6       EVA, 4, 4, 3, 3~6          , X~6        X , 2DeCoso~6          , mandos~6       100, oConso~6~6    <layout of mandos>~6       EVA, 4, 4, 3, 3~6          ,          ,         ,        ,           , X,~6          , bNewTrazo, bEdit -, bEdit +, bDel Points,  ,  bDump~6          , lTolerancia, eTole, bReduce, rgTintas, -, bSave~6~6#listix#~6~6   <main>~6      MSG, 2DeCoso setStyle, tinta1~6~6   <-- rgTintas>~6       MSG, 2DeCoso setStyle, @<rgTintas selected.value>~6~6~6    <-- bNewTrazo>     MSG, 2DeCoso newTrazo~6    <-- bEdit ->       MSG, 2DeCoso incCurrentTrazo, -1~6    <-- bEdit +>       MSG, 2DeCoso incCurrentTrazo, 1~6    <-- bDel Points>   MSG, 2DeCoso modeDelPoints~6    <-- bReduce>~6       -->, 2DeCoso control!, REDUCTION_TOLERANCE, @<eTole>~6       MSG, 2DeCoso reducePoints, @<eTole>~6~6    <-- bDump>~6          MSG, oConso clear~6          MSG, 2DeCoso dump~6~6#data#~6~6   <rgTintas orientation> X~6   <rgTintas>~6        label , value, selected~6        notinta , notinta~6        tinta1  , tinta1   , 1~6        tinta2  , tinta2   ,~6        tinta3  , tinta3   ,~6~6    <eTole> 3~6    <2DeCoso REDUCTION_TOLERANCE> 3~6    <2DeCoso MIN_DISTANCE_TWO_PTS> 5~6    <2DeCoso EDIT_POINT_RECT> 6~6    <2DeCoso trazos>~6      defstyle, editCurrentTrazo, ~3fc:none;sc:yellow;sw:2~3~6      defstyle, tinta1, ~3fc:+188188188;sw:1~3~6      defstyle, tinta2, ~3fc:+123123123;sw:1~3~6      defstyle, tinta3, ~3fc:+067067067;sw:1~3~6      defstyle, notinta, ~3fc:none;sw:1~3');
INSERT INTO tGastExamples VALUES ('z2DCebolla', 'trazaCaballo', '~#javaj#~6~6    <frames> f1, Traza caballo, 800, 700~6~6    <layout of f1>~6       EVA, 4, 4, 3, 3~6          , X~6        X , 2DeCoso~6          , mandos~6       100, oConso~6~6    <layout of mandos>~6       EVA, 4, 4, 3, 3~6          ,          ,         ,        ,           , X,~6          , bNewTrazo, bEdit -, bEdit +, bDel Points, , bSave, bLoad, bDump~6          , lTolerancia, eTole, bReduce,~6~6#listix#~6~6    <-- bNewTrazo>     MSG, 2DeCoso newTrazo~6    <-- bEdit ->       MSG, 2DeCoso incCurrentTrazo, -1~6    <-- bEdit +>       MSG, 2DeCoso incCurrentTrazo, 1~6    <-- bDel Points>   MSG, 2DeCoso modeDelPoints~6    <-- bReduce>       MSG, 2DeCoso reducePoints, @<eTole>~6    <-- bDump>~6          MSG, oConso clear~6          MSG, 2DeCoso dump~6    <-- bSave>~6       MSG, 2DeCoso flushTrazos~6       DUMP, data, :mem garda, 2DeCoso trazos~6    <-- bLoad>~6       VAR=, 2DeCoso trazos, ~3~3~6       LOAD, data, :mem garda~6       MSG, 2DeCoso data!~6~6#data#~6~6    <eTole> 12~6    <2DeCoso MIN_DISTANCE_TWO_PTS> 12~6    <2DeCoso EDIT_POINT_RECT> 6~6    <2DeCoso trazos>~6       defstyle, pel, ~3fc:+255127039~3~6       defstyle, pelo, ~3fc:+234234234~3~6~6       z ,238, 121, ~3pel~3, //jau,84,39,109,-20,47,23,-6,54,-22,20,-35,25,-68,29,-75,1,-54,-29,-31,-81~6       z ,196, 223, ~3pel~3, //jau,-43,-81,-10,-36,9,-19,39,8,64,37~6       z ,155, 84, ~3pel~3, //jau,-47,7,-34,48,-16,29,20,19,36,-29,40,-15~6       z ,468, 148, ~3pel~3, //jau,26,22,14,27,1,46,-5,49,12,56,-12,73,-7,33,-25,0,13,-32,-10,-93,-45,-57,-16,-49~6       z ,196, 213, ~3pel~3, //jau,4,52,29,42,18,65,0,54,-12,28,10,4,18,-1,-2,-18,11,-18,-4,-85,5,-86~6       z ,473, 152, ~3pelo~3, //jau,51,14,23,59,8,86,-10,0,-3,27,-12,-28,5,38,-11,-2,-6,-37,5,-80,-11,-45,-19,-14~6       z ,128, 83, ~3pel~3, //jau,-22,-23,3,31~6       z ,123, 83, ~3pelo~3, //jau,44,-3,65,19,28,27,30,25,-20,19,6,13,-15,-3,-7,-26,-13,7,-17,-24,-28,-28,-21,4,-23,-20,-31,-9');
INSERT INTO tGastExamples VALUES ('z2DCebolla', 'trazaToBrowserDemo', '~#data#~6~6   <laData>~6      // var vdata = {~6      //      ~3Caballo graffiti~3: [~6      //    [ ~3defstyle~3, ~3piel~3, ~3fc:#ff7f27~3 ],~6      //    [ ~3defstyle~3, ~3pelo~3, ~3fc:#eaeaea~3],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,238, 121, ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,84,39,109,-20,47,23,-6,54,-22,20,-35,25,-68,29,-75,1,-54,-29,-31,-81 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,196, 223, ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,-43,-81,-10,-36,9,-19,39,8,64,37 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,155, 84,  ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,-47,7,-34,48,-16,29,20,19,36,-29,40,-15 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,468, 148, ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,26,22,14,27,1,46,-5,49,12,56,-12,73,-7,33,-25,0,13,-32,-10,-93,-45,-57,-16,-49 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,196, 213, ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,4,52,29,42,18,65,0,54,-12,28,10,4,18,-1,-2,-18,11,-18,-4,-85,5,-86 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,473, 152, ~3pelo~3,  ~3jau~3,51,14,23,59,8,86,-10,0,-3,27,-12,-28,5,38,-11,-2,-6,-37,5,-80,-11,-45,-19,-14 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,128, 83,  ~3piel~3,  ~3jau~3,-22,-23,3,31 ],~6      //    [ ~3z~3 ,123, 83,  ~3pelo~3,  ~3jau~3,44,-3,65,19,28,27,30,25,-20,19,6,13,-15,-3,-7,-26,-13,7,-17,-24,-28,-28,-21,4,-23,-20,-31,-9 ],~6      //    ],~6      // };~6      //~6~6#listix#~6~6   <main>~6      MICO, ONCE~6~6   <GET />~6      //<html>~6      //<body>~6      //      <canvas width=~3400~3 height=~3400~3 id=~3Caballo~3></canvas>~6      //      <svg width=~3400~3 height=~3400~3 id=~3Caballo~3></svg>~6      //<script>~6      //~6      //@<:infile META-GASTONA/js/trazos2D-min.js>~6      //~6      // @<laData>~6      //~6      //   window.onload = function(e)~6      //   {~6      //      trazos2D ().renderSvgGraffitis (vdata);~6      //      trazos2D ().renderCanvasGraffitis (vdata);~6      //   };~6      //~6      //</script>~6      //</body>~6      //</html>');INSERT INTO tZWidgetAttributes VALUES ('z2DCebolla', 'visible', 'in', '0 / 1', 'Value 0 to make the widget not visible');
