INSERT INTO tGastExamples VALUES ('z2DMiRelos', 'mirelos sample', '~#javaj#~6~6    <frames> main,~6~6    <layout of main>~6       EVA, 4, 4, 3, 3~6          , X~6        X , 2DjMiRelos~6~6#data#~6~6    <2DjMiRelos backGroundShape>~6      z ,80, 50, ~3sc:none~3, //jau, 480, 480~6      z ,332, 119, ~3fc:#E68A00~3, //jauz,96,34,58,115,-30,123,-113,70,-119,-58,-32,-117,36,-98~6~6    <2DjMiRelos hoursShape>~6       z ,316, 269, ~3fc:#E6E600~3, //jau,65,-10,1,-13,39,23,-17,25,-13,-12,-54,16,-13,0,-9,-27~6~6    <2DjMiRelos minutesShape>~6       z ,309, 296, ~3fc:#E6E600~3, //jau,39,0,2,-13,-11,-119,26,1,-32,-36,-38,27,23,15,-5,122~6~6    <2DjMiRelos secondsShape>~6       z ,330, 280, ~3~3, //jau,10,-13,-31,-52,25,-23,-11,-39,10,-26,-4,-40,-10,26,26,0,-16,-26~6~6    <2DjMiRelos axisShape>~6       z ,322, 280, ~3fc:#CC3300~3, //jau,13,-9,-4,13~6~6    <2DjMiRelos axisPosition>~6~7~7    322, 280~6~6    <2DjMiRelos referenceTime> 03:00:00');INSERT INTO tZWidgetAttributes VALUES ('z2DMiRelos', 'visible', 'in', '0 / 1', 'Value 0 to make the widget not visible');
